ProtoResult:
. "The series $\sum ^\infty_{n=k} a_nb_n$ converges if 
   $\lim_{n\to\infty} a_n= 0$ \begin{equation} \sum 
   |a_{n+1}-a_n|<\infty, \end{equation} and \begin{equation} 
   |b_k+b_{k+1}+\cdots+b_n|\le M,\quad n\ge k, \end{equation} 
   for some constant $M$"
